			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>The scene of daring adventure woven into this tapestry inspires you as you look on it.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Wondrous Item</b><b>:</b> Uncommon</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>To use this item's other properties, you must spend at least 5 minutes doing nothing but studying it. You can do so only once per day.</li>\n<li>For one hour after you study the tapestry, while you are within 10 squares of it, you can make saving throws against charm effects and fear effects at the start and end of each of your turns.</li>\n<li>For one hour after you study the tapestry, while you are within 10 squares of it, you can reroll any damage die that has a result of 1.</li>\n</ul></p>",
